        {
            "title": "有片｜黑衣男「大地任我行」 橫越龍翔道6條行車線 網民批：有天橋有行人隧道都要咁",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<div id=\"vdo-player-container\">\n<video class=\"video-js vjs-default-skin\" controls=\"\" id=\"vdo-player\" muted=\"\" playsinline=\"\" poster=\"\" width=\"100%\">\n<source src=\"https://video.hkhl.hk/90b2b3381d0871f0b2305014c1ca0102/0f43ec15a5f84af4a9090387ec5e8743-b70efbc7379202e01ad762b999f21439-ld.mp4\" type=\"video/mp4\">\n                        Your browser does not support the video tag.\n                    </source></video>\n<div class=\"vdo-ad-container web\" data-vslot=\"vod_ad\" id=\"div-gpt-vad-680383f93335b\"></div>\n<div class=\"vdo-ad-container mweb\" data-vslot0=\"vod_ad,2\" id=\"div-gpt-vad-680383f93335d\"></div>\n</div>\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/5d0a18172a12321cb44a15cd635d6513/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250419/_2025041918140196918.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\"></figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>馬路如虎口，但仍然有不少人貪方便，亂過馬路。有網民今日（19日）上載兩條影片至社交平台，見到一名男子竟在車來車往的龍翔道，一口氣橫跨6條行車線，有司機驚見後急忙響咹警示。上載片段的網民批評該名男子行為魯莽，「有天橋有行人隧道都要咁過馬路，以為自己賽跑冠軍」。\n\n</p>\n<p>有關車cam未有顯示事發日期及時間，片中見到一名身穿黑色上衣的男子，從黃大仙中心對開衝出馬路，橫越龍翔道3條西行線，當時車流在他身旁穿過，有司機亦急忙響咹警示，場面驚險，惟男子未有停下，反而攀過路中石壆後，趁沒有車駛至時，急忙橫越東行線的3條行車線。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4204307/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"一名身穿黑色上衣的男子，從黃大仙中心對開衝出馬路，橫越龍翔道3條西行線。網上片段截圖\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/ff7b39d97d4e6ea3071f2bb3f51879b4/2025-04/AQPlaP9josgVVhoX7fLN_ddGOAMGNkF026hJaCkRnzQ6Mbuil67aCO58JP94TneUGEV_5JTTNnAy2Vx6tmYuGKdD_mp4_snapshot_00_02_383.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        一名身穿黑色上衣的男子，從黃大仙中心對開衝出馬路，橫越龍翔道3條西行線。網上片段截圖\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4204306/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"一名身穿黑色上衣的男子，從黃大仙中心對開衝出馬路，橫越龍翔道3條西行線。網上片段截圖\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/8fba8d5fc1cfc27b1da2bcefcd601d8f/2025-04/AQPlaP9josgVVhoX7fLN_ddGOAMGNkF026hJaCkRnzQ6Mbuil67aCO58JP94TneUGEV_5JTTNnAy2Vx6tmYuGKdD_mp4_snapshot_00_03_705.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        一名身穿黑色上衣的男子，從黃大仙中心對開衝出馬路，橫越龍翔道3條西行線。網上片段截圖\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4204305/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"一名身穿黑色上衣的男子，從黃大仙中心對開衝出馬路，橫越龍翔道3條西行線。網上片段截圖\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/19cf280c5224aa8152995885ddae3747/2025-04/AQPlaP9josgVVhoX7fLN_ddGOAMGNkF026hJaCkRnzQ6Mbuil67aCO58JP94TneUGEV_5JTTNnAy2Vx6tmYuGKdD_mp4_snapshot_00_05_647.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        一名身穿黑色上衣的男子，從黃大仙中心對開衝出馬路，橫越龍翔道3條西行線。網上片段截圖\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4204304/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"男子攀過路中石壆後，趁沒有車駛至時，急忙橫越東行線的3條行車線。網上片段截圖\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/ae5368464c2138769c8ba790f7a8a76d/2025-04/AQMlovRlEiPd2Gb2At5CJRr8YASBb1QiklPIUGasY-3Tte6YNGQ0BUK93xrcmXheh3N6UoPmKxvaiZsChqdq7C6n_mp4_snapshot_00_00_320.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        男子攀過路中石壆後，趁沒有車駛至時，急忙橫越東行線的3條行車線。網上片段截圖\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4204303/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"男子攀過路中石壆後，趁沒有車駛至時，急忙橫越東行線的3條行車線。網上片段截圖\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/7c65b9dc9c705f25a797464cee17e967/2025-04/AQMlovRlEiPd2Gb2At5CJRr8YASBb1QiklPIUGasY-3Tte6YNGQ0BUK93xrcmXheh3N6UoPmKxvaiZsChqdq7C6n_mp4_snapshot_00_01_128.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        男子攀過路中石壆後，趁沒有車駛至時，急忙橫越東行線的3條行車線。網上片段截圖\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4204302/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"男子攀過路中石壆後，趁沒有車駛至時，急忙橫越東行線的3條行車線。網上片段截圖\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/cd58ad0caecce8ff3b28bb5aa09a787e/2025-04/AQMlovRlEiPd2Gb2At5CJRr8YASBb1QiklPIUGasY-3Tte6YNGQ0BUK93xrcmXheh3N6UoPmKxvaiZsChqdq7C6n_mp4_snapshot_00_02_050.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        男子攀過路中石壆後，趁沒有車駛至時，急忙橫越東行線的3條行車線。網上片段截圖\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<p>據了解，現場100米外有一條行人天橋供市民橫跨龍翔道，上載片段的網民批評該名男子行徑魯莽，「有天橋有行人隧道都要咁過馬路，以為自己賽跑冠軍」。其後有網民亦指男子的行為隨時累及司機，「害死司機系列」、「罰五千就啱」、「遲早一鑊，希望司機無事」、「快啲報警好過啦！呢度三線行車路嚟㗎」。<br/>\n \n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
