            "title": "NBA附加賽｜熱火爆冷擊敗鷹隊 奪東岸第8種子創多項紀錄",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"熱火爆冷擊敗鷹隊，奪東岸第8種子創多項紀錄。AP\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/9c8d4c8170010cdda1257c7b15da3d1d/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250419/_2025041918122763080.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">熱火爆冷擊敗鷹隊，奪東岸第8種子創多項紀錄。AP</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>希路(Tyler Herro)於周五的NBA東岸常規賽附加賽獨取30分，包括於加時投進兩個3分球，協助熱火作客加時123:114擊敗鷹隊，奪得東岸季後賽第8種子席位，並改寫多項紀錄，包括成為首支以常規賽第10名打入季後賽的球隊。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"熱火(白衫)爆冷擊敗鷹隊。AP\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/bbb9910e47fe5e345544615f7bbb6fe2/2025-04/Heat_Hawks_Basketball_28942--7fd39.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        熱火(白衫)爆冷擊敗鷹隊。AP\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"熱火(白衫)爆冷擊敗鷹隊。AP\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/d84f66a08ad75091e74a6e3882925d40/2025-04/Heat_Hawks_Basketball_62653--5dbe8.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        熱火(白衫)爆冷擊敗鷹隊。AP\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"希路連續兩仗投進30分或以上。AP\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/0ec32cbd6fdc6c85ec531c66bd4c6d1b/2025-04/Heat_Hawks_Basketball_01200--78f5d.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        希路連續兩仗投進30分或以上。AP\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"熱火(白衫)爆冷擊敗鷹隊。AP\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/f02765dda35b5543beae775672c1d45f/2025-04/Heat_Hawks_Basketball_79534--b3dc6.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        熱火(白衫)爆冷擊敗鷹隊。AP\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"希路(右)連續兩仗投進30分或以上。AP\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/b5110fc07f13f3d682b30c2fb1a76ddb/2025-04/Heat_Hawks_Basketball_49606--e93cc.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        希路(右)連續兩仗投進30分或以上。AP\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"希路(左)連續兩仗投進30分或以上。AP\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/7afa1e863cf32813ddc60c755b83df57/2025-04/Heat_Hawks_Basketball_58563--6a0d4.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        希路(左)連續兩仗投進30分或以上。AP\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"希路跌落地亦不肯放開皮球。AP\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/14db16f2dc86fa013f85801134d84af5/2025-04/APTOPIX_Heat_Hawks_Basketball_26881--0de37.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        希路跌落地亦不肯放開皮球。AP\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"希路連續兩仗投進30分或以上。AP\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/54bee7a613d9602a061930611c347668/2025-04/Heat_Hawks_Basketball_38107--0e92b.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        希路連續兩仗投進30分或以上。AP\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p><h2>希路附加賽發威</h2>\n<p>以東岸第10名出戰附加賽的熱火，在附加賽全靠得分後衛希路支撐大局，他繼附加賽首圈作客第9名的公牛交出38分之後，今仗作客鷹隊他又貢獻全隊最高的30分，包括於加時投進兩個重要的3分球。隊友當路雲米曹(Davion Mitchell)加時亦投進3個3分球，兩人已包辦熱火加時17分中的15分。\n\n</p><h2>熱火連續3年透過附加賽打季後賽</h2>\n<p>反觀，鷹隊得分主力楊格(Trae Young)在加時只投進5分，並有一次失誤，未能阻止鷹隊以9分敗給熱火，無緣季後賽。而熱火於附加賽接連擊敗常規賽第9名公牛和第8名鷹隊，成為首支晉級季後賽的第10名球隊。同時，熱火還創下連續3年通過附加賽晉身季後賽的紀錄；又追平湖人3次經過附加賽晉身季後賽的紀錄。\n\n</p><h2>史普士查有信心對騎士再創奇蹟</h2>\n<p>熱火以東岸第8種子晉身季後賽，首圈會硬撼騎士。熱火練史普士查(Erik Spoelstra)賽後興奮表示：「我很清楚球員有多渴望出戰季後賽，能夠從他們的眼神看到，亦可從內心感受到。」展望首圈對騎士，史普士查說：「很高興可以打入季後賽，我們成為第一支作客連贏兩場晉身季後賽，之前沒有人做到，我們要證明什麼都有可能！」\n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
