            "title": "川男網購近視眼鏡  配戴4天視網膜脫落  商家只賠......",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"川男網購近視眼鏡，配戴4天感不適竟視網膜脫落險失明。\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/efac91b4c743d6a8adcd84803b12fd1f/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250419/_2025041918173347078.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">川男網購近視眼鏡，配戴4天感不適竟視網膜脫落險失明。</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>四川省1名男子，2024年網購1副「寶島眼鏡」出產的近視眼鏡，沒想到配戴眼鏡後，他的右眼出現不適，到醫院檢查後竟是視網膜脫離。事後男子發現這副眼鏡的散光軸位存在落差。男子要求寶島眼鏡賠償，對此寶島眼鏡客服表示，配戴眼鏡不會造成視網膜脫落，且眼鏡的誤差在國家標準範圍內。\n\n</p><h2>眼鏡公司只願賠20元</h2>\n<p>據內媒報道，去年，四川的小翟（化名）在寶島眼鏡旗艦店網購了一副近視眼鏡，剛戴就感覺拉扯感明顯，客服讓他「先適應一下」。3天後，他越來越難受，右眼飄黑影，去醫院發現「右眼視網膜脫離」，需要立刻手術！眼鏡拿到寶島門店檢測後：該眼鏡的散光軸位為10，而他下單備註的軸位為5，被認為製作存在誤差。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"網購近視眼鏡出事，川男配戴4天視網膜脫落險失明。 黑貓投訴\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/28d9cdc060862ba447d311406dcba939/2025-04/vlcsnap-2025-04-19-17h58m21s132.png\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        網購近視眼鏡出事，川男配戴4天視網膜脫落險失明。 黑貓投訴\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"網購近視眼鏡出事，川男配戴4天視網膜脫落險失明。 黑貓投訴\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/f4e5888d984b8b02ba0f9a5d49fb4da5/2025-04/vlcsnap-2025-04-19-17h58m28s156.png\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        網購近視眼鏡出事，川男配戴4天視網膜脫落險失明。 黑貓投訴\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"眼鏡公司只願賠20元人民幣。 黑貓投訴\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/4429b12d7e3e1fc382e1cfc63e00013a/2025-04/vlcsnap-2025-04-19-17h58m47s424.png\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        眼鏡公司只願賠20元人民幣。 黑貓投訴\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"川男網購的近視眼鏡。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/8f7a3db82b86e0068446da80a1c7af44/2025-04/vlcsnap-2025-04-19-17h58m59s161.png\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        川男網購的近視眼鏡。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"商家回答川男查詢。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/548b77edea3afd314bfee40920b113e8/2025-04/vlcsnap-2025-04-19-17h59m15s477.png\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        商家回答川男查詢。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"該眼鏡的散光軸位為10，而川男下單備註的軸位為5。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/71465c87136075da012246a2286947c3/2025-04/vlcsnap-2025-04-19-17h59m28s627.png\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        該眼鏡的散光軸位為10，而川男下單備註的軸位為5。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"商家回答川男查詢。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/aee2066ef56e4afb7492224e85c8d81a/2025-04/vlcsnap-2025-04-19-17h59m35s243.png\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        商家回答川男查詢。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"川男網購近視眼鏡，配戴4天視網膜脫落。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/8babc05680302d332ddb8c6bc04cef33/2025-04/vlcsnap-2025-04-19-17h59m46s121.png\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        川男網購近視眼鏡，配戴4天視網膜脫落。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<p>小翟稱視網膜脫落成了諸多不可逆的後遺症，如飛蚊症，永久視野缺損等。如果沒及時手術，很可能有失明風險。術後他3個月不能碰電子產品，期間丟了工作，無法正常生活，陷入嚴重抑鬱，他覺得自己再也開心不起來了。直到現在，他眼前還24小時有黑影抖動。\n\n</p>\n<p>對此，寶島眼鏡提出可以賠償20元人民幣，拒絕退貨退款。客服表示，佩戴眼鏡不會讓視網膜脫落，且該眼鏡存在的誤差在國標範圍之內。\n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
